myprojects.title: Pathway
myprojects.description: Introducing Pathway, your ultimate companion in the quest for your dream career. With a user-friendly interface and powerful search capabilities, Pathway makes finding your next job a breeze. Explore thousands of job listings from top companies, tailored to your preferences and skills. Our intuitive tools allow you to easily apply for jobs, track your applications, and manage your job search effortlessly.

myprojects.title: CrowdSurf
myprojects.description: CrowdSurf is a web-based platform designed to help users discover exciting events and purchase tickets conveniently based on their location.

myprojects.title: Team Profile Generator
myprojects.description: Enabling Manager users to generate a webpage that displays their team's basic information so that they have a quick access to the team member's emails and GitHub profiles.

myprojects.title: Weather Dashboard
myprojects.description: Enabling travellers to search cities and getting 5 day weather forecast so that they can plan their trips accordingly.

myprojects.title: Learn about Leap Year
myprojects.description: Welcome to Leap Year celebration! An intuitive tool to find out which years are Leap Years with a friendly leap year frog.

myprojects.title: Work Day Scheduler
myprojects.description: An interactive task scheduler for employees during business hours so that they can manage their day effectively.
